Title: String
Description\n: The requirement response must be of type string\n

Title: Date-time
Description\n: The requirement response must be of type date-time (ISO8601)\n

Title: Number
Description\n: The requirement response must be of type number i.e. a floating point or whole number\n

Title: Integer
Description\n: The requirement response must be of type integer\n

Title: Boolean
Description\n: The requirement response must be of type boolean\n

Title: Value
Description\n: The requirement response must be of type value object\n
